1.1.0.name: wordpress/list-site-contributors
1.1.0.description:
List site contributors allows you list your site's contributors and authors. Just add the shortcode [listsitecontributors] to a page on your blog. Optionally you can use the User Photo Plugin (http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/user-photo/) for images,
otherwise Avatars will be used.
